attributes.name: Name Your Strap - 1 icon
attributes.description: From today on it is possbile to create your own strap from AIGNER and decorate and individualize it by yourself! With the help of our online tool we make "NAME YOUR STRAP" possible. Decide between a large selection of options how your very own design of your strap should look alike. You can choose by a range of 10 colours like Pink, Ruby Red, Nude, White, Orange, Moss Green and Marine, as well as Burgundy, Taupe and Black the main colour of the strap. In an eye-catching contrast two symbols are used as decorations in the the same color selection as the letters. You can select the letters from A to Z, the number sequence from 0 to 9, as also a symbol of a heart and the AIGNER logo itself. The color of the seams on the letters and the back of the strap will be the same. The colour of the logo and the heart can both be chosen separetely in two different colours. To create an either exciting or even particularly special look, we also offer to decide where to put all the icons. So therefore we leave it open to you to either attach all symbols, numbers or letters on the left side, the middle or the right side of the strap. Finally  you can choose the colour of the metal parts: silver or light gold shiny. The strap is made of the finest cowhide leather in Italy, who is a partner for many years and know the brand very well. All the icons are sewn on by hand onto the cowhide strap. For this reason the production can last up to 1 to 2 months, because each strap is made individually by traditional craftmanship for each customer. This strap can be decorated with 1 icon.

customFields.articleDetails: Shoulder strap with 1 icon| Length: 90 cm| width: 4 cm| Metal parts: Light gold shining
